<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">A group of beautiful islands within the southern section of the Windward Islands.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Bequia</b> - </font></font><a href="http://bequiatourism.com/island.htm"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://bequiatourism.com/island.htm</font></a><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">, </font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g1480284-Port_Elizabeth_Bequia_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g1480284-Port_Elizabeth_Bequia_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html</font></a><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">, </font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147383-d150060-Reviews-Lower_Bay_Beach-Bequia_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147383-d150060-Reviews-Lower_Bay_Beach-Bequia_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Bequia is one of the largest of the islands within the Grenadines.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>It has many attractions such as good diving and snorkelling, the turtle sanctuary, beautiful beaches, good hiking, shops, restaurants and bars</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Mayreau</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147386-d148225-Reviews-Salt_Whistle_Bay-Mayreau_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147386-d148225-Reviews-Salt_Whistle_Bay-Mayreau_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html</font></a><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">, </font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g147386-Mayreau_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g147386-Mayreau_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Mayreau is a lovely island with a great view point overlooking the Tobago Cays.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Saltwhistle Bay should not be missed.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>It is a beautiful coconut tree lined bay with gorgeous turquoise waters to swim in.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Canouan</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g580455-Canouan_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g580455-Canouan_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Has a golf course and a 5* resort but for us is a great snorkel and dive location.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Mustique</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g147385-Mustique_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g147385-Mustique_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html</font></a><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">, </font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147385-d3207717-Reviews-Basil_s_Bar_Mustique-Mustique_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147385-d3207717-Reviews-Basil_s_Bar_Mustique-Mustique_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Is where many very rich have their lovely houses.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>It has a beautiful beach called Macaroni beach on the Atlantic side.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Red toed tortoises roam the island freely and its one of the few places where you can find many torpedo rays.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>St Vincent</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g147380-St_Vincent_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g147380-St_Vincent_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Has a volcano which is a great hiking location.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>It has the film set for Pirates of the Caribbean at Wallilabou.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>It also has some of the best diving in the Caribbean.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Tobago Cays</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147379-d148334-Reviews-Tobago_Cays-St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147379-d148334-Reviews-Tobago_Cays-St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html</font></a><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">, </font><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tobago_Cays"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tobago_Cays</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Beautiful, Beautiful, Beautiful. 4 small islands with no buildings.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>A marine park where many turtles can be seen swimming freely.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Sting Rays are common as are all the other tropical fish.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Great diving and snorkelling.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Large iguanas and red toed tortoises can also be found here.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Petite Martinique</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147295-d263208-Reviews-Petite_Martinique-Grenada.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147295-d263208-Reviews-Petite_Martinique-Grenada.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Is one of the main areas for local boat building.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Petit St Vincent</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Hotel_Review-g1408079-d151391-Reviews-Petit_St_Vincent_Resort-Petit_St_Vincent_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Hotel_Review-g1408079-d151391-Reviews-Petit_St_Vincent_Resort-Petit_St_Vincent_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Is a private high class resort with beautiful beaches for everyone to use.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Palm Island</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147379-d149778-Reviews-Palm_Island-St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147379-d149778-Reviews-Palm_Island-St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Another private high class resort with beautiful beaches for everyone to use.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Union Island</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g1005981-Union_Island_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g1005981-Union_Island_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines-Vacations.html</font></a><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">, </font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g1005981-d2525710-Reviews-Chatham_Bay-Union_Island_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g1005981-d2525710-Reviews-Chatham_Bay-Union_Island_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html</font></a><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">, </font><a href="http://www.paradise-islands.org/grenadines/union-island.htm"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.paradise-islands.org/grenadines/union-island.htm</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Is the southern gateway into St Vincent and The Grenadines.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Close to Tobago Cays.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>It has some lovely walks and may beaches where turtles come to lay their eggs.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Its western outer reef also protects Happy Island, a man-made island great for watching the sun set from with a rum punch in your hand.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Chatham Bay on the eastern side is also great for snorkelling and diving.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Ronde Island</b> - </font></font><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ronde_Island"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ronde_Island</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Is the largest private island for sale.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>A good resting point between Grenada and Carriacou.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Carriacou</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147384-d2292264-Reviews-Simply_Carriacou-Carriacou_Island_Grenada.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147384-d2292264-Reviews-Simply_Carriacou-Carriacou_Island_Grenada.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Is a friendly Carribean island in the northern area of Grenada.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>There are some beautiful islands off the southern coast. </font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Grenada </b>- </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g147295-Grenada-Vacations.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Tourism-g147295-Grenada-Vacations.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Is a lush tropical island full of natural beauty.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>It is well known for rum and spice.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Petit Tabac</b> -<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></font></font><a href="http://www.paradise-islands.org/grenadines/tobago-cays-petit-tabac.htm"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.paradise-islands.org/grenadines/tobago-cays-petit-tabac.htm</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">A beautiful flat palm tree and scrub island where a scene from pirates of the Carribean was filmed.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Recently a section of a Russian rocket was washed up on the island.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>It has good snorkelling.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Sandy Island</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147384-d150172-Reviews-Sandy_Island-Carriacou_Island_Grenada.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147384-d150172-Reviews-Sandy_Island-Carriacou_Island_Grenada.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">An idyllic deserted sandy island with some good snorkelling.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Happy Island</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.happy-island.info/happy_island_galery.htm"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.happy-island.info/happy_island_galery.htm</font></a><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">, </font><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iDUu0_qZpHk"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iDUu0_qZpHk</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">One of the best places to watch the sun set with a rum punch or beer in your hand.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Mopion</b> - </font></font><a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147380-d564173-Reviews-Mopion-St_Vincent_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html"><font color="#0000ff" face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g147380-d564173-Reviews-Mopion-St_Vincent_St_Vincent_and_the_Grenadines.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Otherwise known as the Engagement Island.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>It is a very small sandy island with a single manmade umbrella on it.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>A “swimming pool” lagoon is protected within a perimeter of corals which are great for snorkelling.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"></font></font>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><o:p></o:p></font></font>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; tab-stops: 51.0pt;"><b><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><b><u><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">HOW TO GET THERE<o:p></o:p></font></font></u></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Check out flights on </font><a href="http://www.opodo.co.uk/"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">www.opodo.co.uk</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Return flight to Grenada from Gatwick typically costs<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; around </span>£650. </font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Virgin Atlantic Flight No VS51 Outbound, depart Gatwick every Thursday at 0935, arriving Grenada 1520 (local time)</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span>VS52 Inbound. Depart Grenada every Thursday 1730, arriving Gatwick at 0840 (+1day local time)</font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Aircraft Type 744</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">American Airlines fly into St Lucia, Barbados and Grenada.&nbsp; We recommend flying into Grenada and catching a Liat flight to St Vincent.&nbsp; Then we take you through the Grenadines and sail you back to Grenada; or you can fly back from Union Island or Carriacou (or take the ferry)&nbsp;and spend the extra time in the gorgeous Grenadines.</font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Grenada to Carriacou Fast Ferry (approx 90 mins)</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><a href="http://www.ospreylines.com/schedule.html"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.ospreylines.com/schedule.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><a href="http://www.svgair.com/carriacou_schedules_and_fares.html"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">http://www.svgair.com/carriacou_schedules_and_fares.html</font></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">Carriacou to Grenada, Flight 185.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Departs Carriacou 2.30pm, arrives Grenada 2.50pm, approx $60US.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p>
